rr Squire<br><img src=http://www.winterblood.com/mmdn/star2.gif></span><br>  Posts: 25<br> <font color=#000000>(6/7/01 4:57:57 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Special thanks to Lords of the Dragon</span><hr size=1> Last night some &lt;Knowledge&gt; guys and I (Quab, Faydakin, Grognik) were going to get the alluring horn in the OOT for the bard epic, things went south when we aggrod too many, and I died.<br>
