<br>
That's the biggest snag on our quest. I personally asked Afterlife if they'd help take down Gorenaire for some platinum, they said 2 for 10 against her, no way sorry. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  I asked Forsaken Realm, same deal that dragon isn't worth the deaths and CR for a uber guild.<br>
<br>
vox, well you have to stay under 52 and try to join the lemmings raid based system for a long time to acquire points to buy a scale. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
so yeah, our epic is way hard unless you have a uber guild to fall back on. Landimal will get his epic no problem though, it'll just take him time. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#E9E9EF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub18.ezboard.com/ulandimal.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Landimal</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>MithMarr Squire<br><img src=http://www.winterblood.com/mmdn/star2.gif></span><br>  Posts: 28<br> <font color=#000000>(6/8/01 1:42:24 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Special thanks to Lords of the Dragon</span><hr size=1> heh Sev, you're right, I'm gonna get that epic if I have to Kite Gore myself.  The cleric epic everyone wants to help out on, because there are about 3 chances to get a redscale/CoF on it (Ixblat, the queen and Ragefire).  The bard epic is mildly retarded for needing the white scale (or the red for that matter).  It makes the biggest obstacle all about $$$, I would never do it, but when you look at the time involved in raising that kind of coin, I can see why people would ebay PP.  <br>
<br>
My method of fund raising: Mow down low level dungeons that drop FS and PP.  I'm on late at night, and I'm the only one in zone when I do it, so I don't see this as such a bad thing.<br>
