<br>
Now, Lemmings says they'd let me organise a vox raid if I wanted, but considering my reputation that's not an option for me, you might want to try it though.<br>
<br>
As for the redscale, same as above for me. I have no guild so raiding the cleric epic mobs with people isn't even an option. <br>
